The A1425 MacBook Pro has great build quality and design, but it isn't invincible. Since your device is of little use when broken, it's a good idea to bring it to iFixYouri for expert Screen Repair.

Screen or LCD Replacement is what you need if your A1425 has a cracked display or your MacBook Pro is displaying horizontal or vertical bars, or nothing at all.
